{"tid":368982,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「冇圖」廢老如何用2蚊爽過李加乘","createTime":"2017-08-22T03:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T08:42:28.000Z","uid":125069,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cbc20f72e7e9677c5e431654c3c5bd8949be2f49","tid":368982,"uid":125069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:13:40.000Z","msg":"今朝有d野做要遲d返工<br />\n本身唔係繁忙時段冇咩人就諗住坐個靚位訓到落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n圈L知唔夠三個站上左個廢老<br />\n佢呀媽個仔一上車就以為自己坐緊7人車<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左對鞋放對十年唔洗既老泥腳去對面個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全地用2蚊坐左4個位<br />\n嚇到我成程車冇訓過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個臭串樣由上車開始冇轉過<br />\n之後幾個站d人上車都行曬上上層<br />\n利申:過海巴士入深山要坐成個鐘，望到禁都唔知中午個餐食唔食得落<br />\nSor for 1999<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/105232_a9596c2bf45a8c2e1c87322fa374db97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F105232_a9596c2bf45a8c2e1c87322fa374db97.jpg&h=22b21e61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/105236_3c0c18ff77993c7ae985807cb6312f29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F105236_3c0c18ff77993c7ae985807cb6312f29.jpg&h=a7bddadb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/105239_6981fc292e6f882f1ccc417988e0b9ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F105239_6981fc292e6f882f1ccc417988e0b9ce.jpg&h=da2edf71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/105240_497adb676b068b28095eed394b155cb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F105240_497adb676b068b28095eed394b155cb5.jpg&h=70e0ad12&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/105241_530aef966af9e6f519858aa4c3ff8c49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F105241_530aef966af9e6f519858aa4c3ff8c49.jpg&h=5f9f629e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nChing們有冇d爆過我既廢老經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93389a674c0c5724a397b097b3938ff99fcc0a6c","tid":368982,"uid":59140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:20:39.000Z","msg":"其實係咪要開聲屌鳩佢呢<br />\n或者搵車長幫手呢"},{"pid":"30f1e2f38e72e344e1487f27cc07c4dd7465a22b","tid":368982,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:28:27.000Z","msg":"個樣好串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b331915d4c1975c6cff240c7815a21beaa3bcb5e","tid":368982,"uid":128287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:37:27.000Z","msg":"呢個廢老我識, 住屯門安定"},{"pid":"a810f15cdb3215a007f9a2972c5604c791644efa","tid":368982,"uid":125069,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪要開聲屌鳩佢呢<br />\n或者搵車長幫手呢</blockquote><br />\n係我冇雷同車長講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我開完post同佢講左句「有冇九両菜」<br />\n佢望左我一眼就繼續自閉mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38efc79ed689e9d71d224da9f63748180536159","tid":368982,"uid":125069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:40:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個樣好串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n憤世既廢老<br />\n我diu7佢之後幾驚佢揼9我"},{"pid":"a5d52ad14646c708dfa3f2667b01d65ac4358faa","tid":368982,"uid":125069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個廢老我識, 住屯門安定</blockquote><br />\n第二頭家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"